This package installs the staged DAPHNE overlay payload into the runtime path
used by `dfx-mgr-client` / `xmutil`.

Installed payload:
- `/lib/firmware/xilinx/daphne_selftrigger_ol_a389fcd/`
- compatibility aliases for the legacy app names used on older boards
- shell.json

Source of truth:
- xilinx/output/
- scripts/package/complete_dtbo_bundle.sh
- scripts/petalinux/stage_overlay_into_project.sh
